<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.4">
<l>pariviṉṟi vāṇaṉaik kāttumeṉ ṟaṉṟu paṭaiyoṭum vantetirnta</l>
<l>tiripurañ ceṟṟava ṉumaka ṉumpiṉṉu maṅkiyum pōrtolaiyap</l>
<l>poruciṟaip puḷḷaik kaṭāviya māyaṉai yāyaṉaip poṉcakkarat</l>
<l>tariyiṉai yaccuta ṉaippaṟṟi yāṉiṟai yēṉu miṭarilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although I am one who has a lord, holding on to the unshakable one, to Hari</l>
<l>with the golden discus, the cowherd, the trickster who drives the bird with beating wings,</l>
<l>so that the one who destroyed the three cities and the son and after [them] Agni lost the battle.</l>
<l>[he] who had come [and] faced [him] with a weapon thinking he would guard Bāṇa without affliction,</l>
	<l>I am without distress.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
